      "content": "the breathing exercises aren't really helping much and the tightness is getting worse. honestly i dont want to go to the hospital if i can avoid it, the wait times are terrible. if i just take some extra dose of my albuterol and maybe some ibuprofen for the tightness, do you think i can just sleep it off? i really think it's just stress/anxiety making it feel worse than it is.",
